<p>Your limelight gives you a value multiplied by a kP. You have lots of unneeded lines of code.</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">If absolutevalue(limelightxvalue) &gt; minDegrees {xadjust = kP*limelightxvalue} else xadjust = 0

